summary:
Upgrades single files or a full havok behavior project to havok version 2010.2.0.r1
will upgrade all hkx files below skyrim havok version to to skyrim havok version
descriptionHtml:
Upgrades single files or a full havok behavior project created with havok behavior tool 6.0 to havok version 2010.2.0.r1
will upgrade all hkx files below skyrim havok version to to skyrim havok version

built around these files AssetCc2.exe and AssetCc1.exe found in havok content tool batch folder
author: theru
